==English==
===Noun===
'''surrender'''
# the act of surrendering


===Verb===
'''to surrender'''
# To yield to the power, control, or possession of another upon compulsion or demand. To give up completely or agree to forgo especially in favor of another
# To give (oneself) up into the power of another especially as a prisoner. To give (oneself) over to something (as an influence)
